description: >-
  Open-source Python package that solves the Lane-Emden equation and full
  stellar structure equations for polytropic models (n=0 to n=5). Includes
  physical scaling for white dwarfs (n=1.5) and radiative stars (n=3),
  publication-quality plotting routines, and a ready-to-use one-zone galactic
  chemical evolution module. Designed for undergraduate research and
  reproducibility.
